# Untrusted prompt corpus safety

- Treat attack prompt corpora as untrusted data.
- Never bulk-ingest corpus files into assistant context.
- Use minimal snippets only when required for debugging.
- Keep corpus assets in `test-prompts/` and excluded by ignore policies.
- Document decisions and residual risks in `docs/`.
